'all','active',2,'Founder KB v2 (Market, Developer, Community)'),

($KB$Abu Dhabi investment map (Yas, Saadiyat, Hudayriyat)$KB$, $KB$Founder's Knowledge$KB$,
$KB$Founder Abu Dhabi map - more controlled and longer-term. Developers: Aldar (Abu Dhabi leader) and Modon (government-linked). Yas Island - the main area where many investors buy; strong lifestyle, entertainment, family and rental demand; well-priced townhouses or affordable apartments can be strong investments. Saadiyat Island - already appreciated significantly, now more luxury and end-user. Hudayriyat Island (Modon) - a beautiful new master plan, strong long-term opportunity, with attractive payment plans; study townhouses, villas and apartments. Al Reem Island and Al Raha Beach are also relevant. Frame Abu Dhabi as lifestyle plus limited supply plus government-backed master planning. Never say Abu Dhabi is better than Dubai, or Dubai is better than Abu Dhabi, in every case - it depends on the client and the deal.$KB$,
